     H            Y.
     F** UEXR35B ***********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: CHECK PT PART BY ZETI (PASS THROUGH)         *
     F*  WRITTEN: J.WATANABE    2020.11.10                     *
     F*--------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR35B'
     F*                    PARM           $ZETI   4
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*  IN  $ZETI :  4A  ABS# (PART#)
     F*  OUT $RTN  :  1A  Y=PT PART, N=NOT PT PART
     F******************************************************
     FFCEPL07 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAAMPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      * GET PART#
     C           $ZETI     CHAINFCEPL07              99
     C   99                GOTO ENDP
      * CHECK AAMPP01
     C                     MOVELA2BHB1    K#SHN1
     C                     MOVELA2BHB2    K#SHN2
     C                     MOVELA2BHB3    K#SHN3
     C           K#PL11    SETLLAAMPL11
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           K#PL11    READEAAMPL11                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           CKSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           CKBM01    IFNE 8990
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           CKKO01    IFNE 'KN '
     C           CKKO01    ANDNE'HN '
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       $RTN
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C           ENDP      TAG
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *======================================================
      * INITIAL SET
      *======================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $ZETI   4
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C           K#PL11    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K#SHN1  5
     C                     KFLD           K#SHN2  5
     C                     KFLD           K#SHN3  2
      *
     C                     MOVE 'N'       $RTN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
